{"tid":2243042,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟番工應該練精學懶，定死做爛做？","createTime":"2020-10-14T12:38:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-15T15:49:30.000Z","uid":57036,"like":201,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"550343a9a4f5a41814a277e72b9517a4ed44659f","tid":2243042,"uid":57036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T12:38:03.000Z","msg":"打份工有邊個唔想多勞多得<br />\n做到成績出黎升職加人工<br />\n但呢個世界唔係一分耕耘一分收穫<br />\n往往你博盡做多幾分都唔一定討好老細<br />\n<br />\n見到有人練精學懶<br />\n事不關己己不勞心<br />\n側側膊咩都話自己唔識<br />\n隔離組問佢野大耍太極<br />\n結果少做少錯<br />\n自己早放工<br />\n仲比腦細讚醒目有效率<br />\n因此佢職場平步青雲<br />\n<br />\n亦見到有人死做爛做<br />\n加上職場大好人<br />\n同事搵佢幫手都有求必應<br />\n隔離組問佢野都幫人地手做埋<br />\n晚晚做到熊貓眼<br />\n結果老細更加放肆地捉佢做野<br />\n甚至覺得佢做得慢<br />\n而deadline仲越黎越緊<br />\n因此佢職場冇咁順暢<br />\n<br />\n唉屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n究竟我仲信唔信一分耕耘一分收穫<br />\n比你揀你會點揀？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />練精學懶<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />死做爛做"},{"pid":"c7de6d4e1138ac2a09d9a33d8d3e58e6234a50d4","tid":2243042,"uid":76341,"like":49,"dislike":1,"score":48,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T12:42:36.000Z","msg":"好簡單 問自己一句 間公司你有無份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b977db75d4755ef604c90d36b0b249d681d2c07","tid":2243042,"uid":230905,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T12:43:28.000Z","msg":"兩睇 當你有啲野放慢做 hea住做 你當然正 如果係要對客 你係個客就梗係唔好受 角色倒轉咁樣諗啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16f406ddcf0e5b662479b4fcab7c7c61c68e9931","tid":2243042,"uid":118945,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T12:45:10.000Z","msg":"